  "title": "Project Manager",
  "description": "<p>Description &amp; Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Prepare and manage project budgets to ensure cost efficiency.</li>\n  <li>Lead and manage project teams, including subcontractors.</li>\n  <li>Liaise and serve as the primary contact between clients, consultants and other stakeholders.</li>\n  <li>Provide regular project updates, monthly progress reports and presentations.</li>\n  <li>Ensure all construction activities meet industry standards, building codes, and client specifications.</li>\n  <li>Ensure strict compliance with safety regulations and protocols on-site.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Civil Engineering, Project / Construction Management or other related discipline</li>\n  <li>Minimum 5 years of relevant experience in construction industry</li>\n  <li>Excellent leadership and communication skills</li>\n</ul>",
